{"word":"ἀπεύχομαι","slug":"ἀπεύχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπεύχομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to wish</i> a thing <i>away, wish</i> it <i>may not happen, deprecate</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>ἀπ. τι γενέσθαι</el> or <el>μὴ γενέσθαι</el> <i>to pray that</i> it <i>may not</i> happen, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to reject, despise</i>, <el>τι</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}